req1: The system shall use A2S6P-C encryption for all stored financial data.
req2: The system shall use AES-256 encryption for all stored financial data.
label: contradiction
reason: Both requirements mandate a specific encryption algorithm for all stored financial data, but they specify different algorithms (A2S6P-C vs. AES-256), making it impossible to satisfy both simultaneously.
